 ('MENS BLADE DF-01 PRO BADMINTON SHOES - WHITE - AYAT005-1', 'The latest new badminton shoes are designed for all aroud badminton players. Dubbed as Blade PRO or DF-01 PRO.The badminton shoes upper is made of low-stretch microfiber leather material, which is soft and comfortable on the upper foot, and the heel is surrounded by TPU to ensure stability during exercise', 2657972, 20, 2),
 ('MENS BADMINTON TRAINING TOP - BLACK - AAYT061-1', 'Introducing the LI-NING Mens Badminton Training Top in black! Designed for serious competitors, this top is perfect for every match. The high-quality material ensures maximum comfort and durability, while the sleek black design adds a touch of style to your game. With its superior breathability and moisture-wicking properties, youll stay cool and dry even during the most intense rallies.', 528933, 20, 1),
 ('MENS BADMINTON COMPETITION TOP - NAVY - AATT021-1', 'Introducing the LI-NING Mens Badminton Competition Top in Navy - AATT021-1. Elevate your game with this high-performance top designed for serious badminton players. Crafted with precision and style, this top is perfect for competitive matches.', 795063, 30, 1),
 ('MENS SAGA II PRO BADMINTON SHOES - STANDARD WHITE - AYAT003-3', 'Move with fluidity across the court when you don the Saga II Pro. The light weight Pro version helps you emulate your power & enhance your footwork with seamless transitions so you can perform at your best. With the cool outer shell and boom incorporated midsole, youll land well even when youre landing heavily.', 2990634, 20, 2);
